summary: Completely out of character voices for the fiercest creatures! Updates regularly.
descriptionHtml:
VIDEO HERE!  http://youtu.be/1RaFlpg2Gu4
 
What happens when I find this website; http://www.sounds-resource.com/
 Crazy shenanigans of course! I couldn\'t resist replacing these voices since it was so easy! 
 All Credit goes to Sounds Resource and Mushroom Kingdom for the voices.
 As I complete and test new voices, they will be added here.
 Sadly, my biggest regret is not being able to obtain the infamous \"Hi, I\'m Daisy\" sound. I have scoured the 4 corners of the web too. If I ever find it, I will put it in ASAP.

HOW TO INSTALL: stick the Sounds folder in your Data folder. Yes, its that easy

Done so far:
Flame Atronach- Princess Peach
Bears- Captain Falcon
Hagraven- Princess Daisy
Wispmother- Princess Rosalina
Troll- Wario
Wolf- Wolf (Star Fox)
author: Astal
